00:36.804 --> 00:38.072
Just hear me out.

00:38.106 --> 00:39.807
than quality?important

00:39.840 --> 00:42.110
Equality.

00:42.143 --> 00:44.345
Now, studies show
that today's woman,

00:44.378 --> 00:46.414
the Ally McBeal woman,
as I call her,

00:46.447 --> 00:47.848
is at a crossroads.

00:47.881 --> 00:49.683
Michael--
And--no, just, I--

00:49.717 --> 00:51.585
You have come
a long way, baby.

00:51.619 --> 00:52.686
But I just...

00:52.720 --> 00:54.788
