01:12.806 --> 01:13.874
We just need you
to leave, please.

01:13.907 --> 01:14.875
Women in the workplace.

01:14.908 --> 01:17.345
Yeah, translation:

01:17.378 --> 01:19.247
I have been banned
from my own conference room

01:19.280 --> 01:21.449
so that Jan can talk in secret
to all the girls.

01:21.482 --> 01:23.751
Oh, sorry.
"Women of the Workplace."

01:23.784 --> 01:25.153
About what?
I don't know.

01:25.186 --> 01:28.156
Clothes, me...

01:28.189 --> 01:28.856
Ick.

01:28.889 --> 01:30.858
Ladies, I am so,

01:30.891 --> 01:31.925
so sorry.

01:31.959 --> 01:34.862
