We were on such a roll.

01:34.895 --> 01:37.131
I-I really apologize
for that.
Jan.

01:37.165 --> 01:37.831
Yes, Pam?

01:37.865 --> 01:39.233
Michael's still
at the door.

01:39.267 --> 01:40.401
Michael!

02:12.500 --> 02:15.403
One obsticle is how
assertiveness

02:15.436 --> 02:17.838
is perceived differently
in men and women.

02:17.871 --> 02:20.741
