02:25.513 --> 02:26.947
What is?

02:26.980 --> 02:28.782
Them in there
all together.

02:28.816 --> 02:30.251
They stay in there
too long,

02:30.284 --> 02:33.554
they're gonna get
on the same cycle.

02:33.587 --> 02:34.755
