on our plumbing.

02:36.957 --> 02:38.259
Everyone, guys...

02:38.292 --> 02:39.427
Circle up, please.

02:39.460 --> 02:41.495
Come on over.
Bring your chairs.

02:41.529 --> 02:43.864
Toby, come on over.

02:43.897 --> 02:46.967
You're a guy...too.
Sort of.

02:47.000 --> 02:48.936
Let's do this.

02:48.969 --> 02:50.604
Well, first of all,

02:50.638 --> 02:52.640
I, uh, just wanna
warm up a little bit.

02:52.673 --> 02:53.674
Let's just clap.

02:53.707 --> 02:55.376
Let's just clap.
Ready?

02:55.409 --> 02:57.345
Yeah!

02:57.378 --> 02:59.580
Yeah! That's what
I'm talkin' about!

02:59.613 --> 03:00.981
I don't know what you're
doing here, Michael.

03:01.014 --> 03:03.884
Just having a little
guys in the workplace thing.

03:03.917 --> 03:06.987
Why can't boys
play with dolls?

03:07.020 --> 03:10.291
