when they met the Others?

04:34.908 --> 04:36.810
I'm so sorry about that.

04:36.844 --> 04:39.079
Um, so where were we?

04:39.112 --> 04:40.848
Pam, are you okay
taking notes then?

04:40.881 --> 04:41.982
Mm-hmm.
Please?

04:42.015 --> 04:44.084
Yeah.
Thank you very much.

04:44.117 --> 04:45.853
So let's meet
the warehouse!

04:45.886 --> 04:48.656
Let's get some shots.

04:48.689 --> 04:50.391
