04:50.424 --> 04:53.661
This is Darrell,
one of our warehouse staff.

04:53.694 --> 04:56.564
Darrell, what is
your biggest fear?

04:56.597 --> 04:58.499
My biggest fear is that
someone will distract us

04:58.532 --> 04:59.967
