05:43.110 --> 05:44.812
A little Good Will Hunting
situation.

05:44.845 --> 05:46.647
All right, troops.

05:46.680 --> 05:49.983
This is...an important day.
A big day.

05:50.017 --> 05:51.952
Now, you may

05:51.985 --> 05:56.123
look around and see
two groups here.

05:56.156 --> 05:57.858
White-collar, blue-collar.

05:57.891 --> 05:59.460
But I don't
see it that way.

05:59.493 --> 06:00.561
