that we know we're good at.

06:09.036 --> 06:12.706
I will start.
I am good at public speaking.

06:12.740 --> 06:14.975
Hi, I'm Meredith,
and I'm an al--

06:15.008 --> 06:16.977
Good at supplier relations.

06:17.010 --> 06:18.446
Great.
Phyllis.

06:18.479 --> 06:20.514
