06:24.452 --> 06:26.119
I don't know.
I thought that...

06:26.153 --> 06:27.621
No, okay, stop.

06:27.655 --> 06:28.989
You know, I've seen
some of your spreadsheets.

06:29.022 --> 06:30.057
And I almost always--
Really?

06:30.090 --> 06:31.525
I thought
they were pretty--

06:31.559 --> 06:33.427
I don't know how I fit in
with these women.

06:33.461 --> 06:35.463
Here.

06:35.496 --> 06:36.930
