06:52.846 --> 06:54.682
you know, you used
to have a crush on Pam.

06:54.715 --> 06:55.749
Oh, no, no, no.

06:55.783 --> 06:56.950
No, no.
No, it's cool.

06:56.984 --> 06:57.851
