so, you know.

07:01.522 --> 07:03.023
We're cool, right?

07:03.056 --> 07:05.859
Yeah.
No, yeah, definitely.

07:05.893 --> 07:06.960
You know,
it's great with me,

07:06.994 --> 07:08.028
'cause that way...

07:08.061 --> 07:09.663
I'm glad she has
a friend at work

07:09.697 --> 07:10.864
