"Bah, bah, bah, bah,"

07:12.232 --> 07:13.200
you know,
when she gets home.

07:13.233 --> 07:14.935
Yeah, I like
talking to her too.

07:14.968 --> 07:16.937
So, uh...
we're cool, right?

07:16.970 --> 07:18.972
Yes. Yeah.

07:19.006 --> 07:19.973
Good.
All right.

07:20.007 --> 07:21.709
Cool, man.
Sweet.

07:28.982 --> 07:30.117
Hey, Mike, look.

07:30.150 --> 07:32.686
How about we go
upstairs, too, you know?

07:32.720 --> 07:34.021
Learn how
an office works.

07:34.054 --> 07:35.656
Oh, well--
We can both switch places
for the day.

07:35.689 --> 07:37.090
Okay, yeah,
you know what?

07:37.124 --> 07:38.859
I don't...you're...

07:38.892 --> 07:40.528
