compared to this.

07:40.561 --> 07:42.195
I don't think
you'd like it up there.
Good experience.

07:42.229 --> 07:43.997
Guys! You wanna start
unloading the truck?

07:45.999 --> 07:48.936
Okay, let's go.
Step up.

07:48.969 --> 07:50.971
Check this out.

07:51.004 --> 07:53.040
Look at that.
Look at that.

07:53.073 --> 07:53.974
Ba boop!

07:54.007 --> 07:55.208
"Hello, how are--"

07:55.242 --> 07:56.744
Okay.

07:58.979 --> 08:00.948
