with three rows of seats.

08:20.568 --> 08:22.035
That would be great.

08:22.069 --> 08:23.136
Well, I'll be honest.
One of the goals

08:23.170 --> 08:24.572
of these women's seminars

08:24.605 --> 08:25.839
is to feel out if there's
any standouts.

08:25.873 --> 08:28.942
