addition to our corporate life.

08:32.780 --> 08:34.682
Michael wants us to bond.

08:34.715 --> 08:36.049
So we need topics
for conversation.

08:36.083 --> 08:37.851
Ponies.

08:37.885 --> 08:38.952
No.

08:38.986 --> 08:39.853
How about rainbows?

08:39.887 --> 08:41.221
No.

08:41.254 --> 08:42.556
Flowers.

08:42.590 --> 08:43.691
That's dangerous,
Michael.

08:43.724 --> 08:44.858
Come on, get down
from there.

08:44.892 --> 08:45.893
