09:54.194 --> 09:55.195
Um...

09:55.228 --> 09:57.064
More seriously, though,

09:57.097 --> 09:59.099
a husband that I love.

09:59.132 --> 10:00.133
Roy.

10:00.167 --> 10:02.102
And...

10:02.135 --> 10:04.104
I love to draw.

10:04.137 --> 10:05.739
And I did a little
in college.

10:05.773 --> 10:06.974
And I'd still
love to do something

10:07.007 --> 10:09.910
where I could work with art
or graphic design in some way.

10:09.943 --> 10:10.944
She's real good.

10:10.978 --> 10:12.913
You know, the company
is offering

10:12.946 --> 10:15.315
a design training program
in New York.

10:15.348 --> 10:16.950
Well, I have a job
right now.

10:16.984 --> 10:18.652
