take time off.

10:18.686 --> 10:20.053
Well, it's--
it's only on weekends.

10:20.087 --> 10:21.188
And then a few weeks
in New York.

10:21.221 --> 10:24.191
But I'm sure that I could
ask corporate to help you out.

10:24.224 --> 10:25.292
Well, it's just that

10:25.325 --> 10:26.927
